Dear Santa...

Dear Santa,

This year I've been busy!

Last Wednesday I ruled Duluth, Minnesota as a cruel and heartless dictator (-700 points). In June I pushed in the mud (-17 points). In May I gave a kidney (1000 points). In July I signed my organ donor card (28 points). In March I gave a wet willie, then I took it back (-5 points).

Overall, I've been nice (306 points). For Christmas I deserve a Lego set!

Sincerely,
eurekamaru101

Dear Santa,

This year I've been busy!

Last Thursday I gave a kidney (1000 points). In November I helped across the street (6 points). Last Friday I helped hide a body (-173 points). In April I gave change to a homeless guy (19 points). In January I gave a wet willie, then I took it back (-5 points).

Overall, I've been nice (847 points). For Christmas I deserve an Easy-Bake Oven!

Sincerely,

I am not currently available right now. However, if you would like to be transferred to another correspondent, please press the number that best fits your personality:

-If you are obsessive compulsive, please press "1" repeatedly.

-If you are codependent, please ask someone to press "2".

-If you have multiple personalities, please press "3", "4", and "5".

-If you are paranoid delusional, we know who you are and what you want. Just stay on the line so we can trace your call.

-If you are schizophrenic, listen carefully and the little voice will tell you which number to press.

-If you are manic depressive, it doesn't matter what number you press, no one will answer.

Pick 12 characters BEFORE you look at my answers! 1. Jack O'Neill 2. Trance Gemini 3. Janet Fraiser 4. Sydney Bristow 5. Daniel Jackson 6. Seamus Harper 7. Tom Paris 8. B'Elanna Torres 9. Kathryn Janeway 10. Rommie 11. Beka Valentine 12. Sam Carter Which would make a better college professor, 6 or 11? What subjects would they teach? Harper or Beka... wow... neither? Well I guess Harper (even though Beka kicks ass) and he would teach Mechanical Engineering Do you think 4 is hot? How hot? ummm if I were male yeah. I can't say how hot only because I am not a male. 12 sends 8 on a mission. What is it, and does it succeed? It would be one of those under cover missions where B'Elanna would have to pretend to be on the bad side and get secrets and eventually blow up the ship... What is or would be 9's favorite book? "7 years in the Delta Quadrant: An Autobigraphy" By: Kathryn Janeway Would it make more sense for 2 to swear fealty to 6 or the other way around? Probably Harper (6) to Trance (2) because I swear in one of those untold stories he already has in "Andromeda" so yeah Harper to Trance (and it wold sooo cute if they were to hook up. For some reason, 5 is looking for a roommate. Should 5 share a studio apartment with 9 or with 10? Rommie probably because Lexa (who plays Rommie) and already freaking married to Micheal (the guy who plays Daniel) so it would just make sense. Although Daniel might have to watch out because Rommie is an android... who knows maybe he'll die again and then he'll miraculously come back to life. 7, 2 and 12 have dinner together. Where do they go, and what do they discuss? ooo tough one... well Trance doesn't eat... Tom eats a lot.... and Sam I see as one of those in between people... so I guess they go to a semi-nice restaurant and discuss how their crew/teams are so freaking annoying. *big eg* 3 challenges 10 to a duel. What happens? Well in NO WAY do i mean to be mean to Janet but Rommie would kick some ass! But that's only because she's an Android and doesn't like get tired or anything like that. If 1 stole 8's most precious possession, how would 8 get it back? B'Elanna would probably bring out her Klingon temper and go kick Jack where the sun don't shine and then they'd fight for a while and it'd probably be a pretty fair fight and then Jack would pull out his in which he always has and will shoot B'Elanna and then she'd end up in the hospital and then Jack being the nice person he is would just give it back. Suggest a title for a story in which 7 and 12 both attain what they most desire. "The Love I Long For" (Tom getting B'Elanna and Sam getting Jack... aww it'd be so sweet!) What kind of plot device would you use if you wanted 4 and 1 to work together? An undercover investigation.. maybe on another planet. If 7 visited you for the weekend, how would you get along? Well let's see in one of my fan fic's he is my dad (I usually write from a perspective and so I was writing from the daughter) and so I guess it would be great. And Tom's a great guy and get's along with anyone. If you could command 3 to perform any one task or service for you, what would it be? Well I guess it would to be my doctor.. and to save me everytime, or does that count as more than one task.... oooo wait I know I have a better one! Get me into the SGC! Does anyone on your friends list write or draw 11? yea at least she did i'm not sure anymore but I know does. If 2 had to choose sides between 4 and 5, which would it be? Trance would choose Daniel because he's nicer than Sydney (or so it seems to me) but that would be purple Trance... now Gold Trance would choose Sydney because she can kick some enemy ass. What might 10 shout while charging into battle? ummm.... "I AM A WARSHIP TOO YOU KNOW!" idk... If you chose a song to represent 8, which song would you choose? ummm... i can't think of any... prob something she can work out with... 1, 6 and 12 are having dim sum at a Chinese restaurant. There is only one scallion pancake left, and they all reach for it at the same time. Who gets to eat it? Harper because would Sam & Jack would have left him at the restaurant HOURS ago... becuase Jack would have gotten annoyed and Harper would have talked all scientifically and Sam would have just been annoyed. What might be a good pick-up line for 2 to use on 10? THAT'S JUST WRONG!!! What would 5 most likely be arrested for? ummm.... for going against direct orders in the Military.. oh wait since he's not technically a part of the military that can't happen.... umm so i guess for being too smart???? What is 6's secret? He's got a sister named Angie whom he left on Earth but then when Harper visited she was still there and clung to him! If 11 and 9 were racing to a destination, who would get there first? Sooooo Beka! Beka's good that way! 3 and 7 tell conflicting versions of events. Which is more reliable? Janet... believe Tom can twist stuff soo much. "1 and 9 reluctantly team up to save the world from the threat posed by 4's sinister secret organization. 11 volunteers to help them, but it is later discovered that 11 is actually a spy for 4. Meanwhile, 4 has kidnapped 12 in an attempt to force their surrender. Following the wise advice of 5, they seek out 3, who gives them what they need to complete their quest." What title would you give this fic? Name three people on your friends list who might read it. Name one person who should write it. Umm The Great Kidnapping? and let's see... and ~or~ would write it!
